OL,3,CDid BBC Breakfast segment cross the
OL,4,Cline regarding product prominence?
OL,6,FAnd they also brought in a copy of
OL,7,Fthis year's Christmas issue to show
OL,8,Foff. It's in the shops on Tuesday,
OL,9,Fthey reminded us.
OL,11,FIf all started to look less about
OL,12,FChristmas TV and more like a naked
OL,13,Fplug for RT.
OL,15,FOn commercial channels, you would have
OL,16,Fwondered if this was paid for product
OL,17,Fplacement.
OL,19,FThere is no suggestion of wrongdoing
OL,20,Fby either RT or the BBC. But did this
OL,21,Fitem end up crossing the line of
OL,22,Feditorial acceptability?
