OL,3,CDid BBC Breakfast segment cross the
OL,4,Cline regarding product prominence?
OL,6,FShould the interviewee have been asked
OL,7,Fto cover up the RT logo on their top?
OL,9,FAnd should they have refrained from
OL,10,Fshowing off this year's Christmas
OL,11,Fissue?
OL,13,FThe rules on items like this need to
OL,14,Fbe explicitly clear. Otherwise we
OL,15,Fcould be on a slippery slope.
OL,17,FDo we want guests nakedly plugging
OL,18,Fother products on BBC programmes?
OL,19,FComplete with branding.
